About Us
A Little Words About Us
The Plumbing Doctor Bakersfield
Your trusted experts for all plumbing needs in Bakersfield and surrounding areas. Our team of licensed, bonded, and insured plumbers are dedicated to providing top-notch service, ensuring your plumbing system is functioning efficiently and effectively.
Services:
Emergency plumbing repairs (available 24/7)
Drain cleaning and sewer line repair
Water heater installation and repair
Toilet installation and repair
Faucet installation and repair
Pipe leaks and slab leak detection
Gas line installation and repair
